title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Sep 16 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Sep 16 2022
description:
Clay sticks to his guns on the superiority of Gulf Coast beaches. What Blake Masters needs to do to beat Astronaut Mark Kelly in the AZ senate race. What happened to Joe Scarborough? Don Lemon insists he wasn't demoted, but he was. Ann Coulter joins Clay and Buck to bust out the verbal jiu-jitsu on the border, crime and the midterms. DeSantis burns Gavin Newsom. Animal Thunderdome!

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
